# Parser Rules

- MarkItDown handles ordinary Office, HTML, XML, JSON, TXT files.
- MinerU handles PDF, images, scans, complex layout and high-value documents.
- Parser output goes under parsed/by_hash/{sha256_prefix}/{sha256}/{parser_profile}/.
- Same content with same parser profile must be idempotent.
